{"data":{"result":{"callId":"chatcmpl-tool-bbd2e658840b5dd6","kind":"tool-result","output":"# Refund eligibility policy\n\nApply these rules in order:\n\n1. **Digital goods** (software, e-books, gift cards): non-refundable once delivered. No exceptions.\n2. **Physical goods, unopened**: full refund within **30 days** of delivery, no fee.\n3. **Physical goods, opened — electronics**: refundable within **30 days**, but a **15% restocking\n   fee** is deducted.\n4. **Physical goods, opened — non-electronics**: refundable within **30 days**, **20% restocking\n   fee**.\n5. **Anything past 30 days**: not refundable (offer store credit at 50% as a courtesy).\n\nAlways state the eligibility decision and the exact fee (if any).\n","toolName":"load_skill"},"sequence":0,"stepIndex":0,"status":"completed","turnId":"turn_0"},"type":"action.result","meta":{"at":"2026-06-18T12:20:16.105Z"}}
